import React from 'react'; import SEO from "../common/SEO"; import {Link} from "react-router-dom"; import { FiArrowRight, FiCheck } from "react-icons/fi"; import HeaderOne from '../common/header/HeaderOne'; import HeaderTopNews from '../common/header/HeaderTopNews'; import FooterTwo from '../common/footer/FooterTwo'; import Copyright from '../common/footer/Copyright'; import ServiceOne from '../elements/service/ServiceOne'; import Separator from "../elements/separator/Separator"; import SectionTitle from "../elements/sectionTitle/SectionTitle"; import SlpitOne from "../elements/split/SlpitOne"; import PortfolioOne from "../elements/portfolio/PortfolioOne"; import TeamFour from "../elements/team/TeamFour"; import BrandTwo from "../elements/brand/BrandTwo"; import ScrollAnimation from "react-animate-on-scroll"; const Accomodations = () => { return ( <>
{/* Start Slider Area */}

Accomodations

  • Our ship is in a class of its own!
  • Take a look at our rooms and the different parts of the ship
Book Now
{/* End Slider Area */} {/* Start Service Area */}
{/* 945 x 709 */}

All of our staterooms include:
  • soft & firm pillows
  • mattress menu
  • queen size or twin bed configuration
  • spacious closet
  • writing desk & chair
  • mini bar
  • hair dryer
  • bathrobe
  • flat screen TV
  • internet/wifi
  • spacious bathroom
  • air conditioning
  • full size mirror
  • large shower with glass door
  • in-room safe
  • 230V power outlets
  • turn down service (on request)
{/* End Service Area */} {/* Start Service Area */}
{/* 945 x 709 */}

Category C: Lower Deck
  • 172 sqft / 16 m2
  • 2 Panoramic Windows
{/* End Service Area */}
{/* 945 x 709 */}

Category K: Middle Deck

R: Upper Deck
  • 200 sqft / 18.6 m2
  • Wall-to-Wall Panoramic Windows
  • French Balcony
  • Seating Area
  • Beds Facing the Window
{/* Start Service Area */}
{/* 945 x 709 */}

Category W: Upper Deck
  • 300 sqft / 27.9 m2
  • Panoramic Sliding Windows
  • French Balcony
  • Large Seating Area
  • Beds Facing the Window
  • Separate Bathroom
{/* End Service Area */} {/* Start Service Area */}
{/* 945 x 709 */}

Category K: Middle Deck

R: Upper Deck
  • Make Up Mirror
  • Power Outlet
  • Spacious Shower with glass door
  • Separate colored towels
  • bath-robe
  • slippers
  • high quality local amenities
{/* End Service Area */}
